      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits moderate wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs fine, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It\u2019s an honest, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the premium price tag.",
