      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this impeccably preserved specimen, which stands as a testament to rigorous maintenance and climate-controlled preservation. This vehicle retains its original showroom luster, exhibiting flawless bodywork and an interior that remains in an untouched state. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically superlative, this unit represents a premier acquisition for the most exacting collector or enthusiast seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
